     H            Y.
     F** VJBR40 **************************************************
     F*  DB REFORMATION (AB#PP66) X                              *
     F*  T.SAKAKI        11/04/2015                              *
     F*  FUNCTION: PURGE RECORD BY DESIGNATED DATE               *
     F*          : PURGED RECORD WILL BE MOVED OUT TO FAB#PP66B  *
     F*----------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQUENCE
     F*                    CALL 'VJBR40'
     F*                    PARM           $DATE   8
     F*                    PARM           $BFR    7
     F*                    PARM           $AFR    7
     F*  IN  $DATE: 8A DATE (YYYYMMDD) PURGE IF A6NYMD =< $DATE
     F*  OUT $BFR : 7A RECORD BEFORE RUN
     F*      $AFR : 7A RECORD AFTER  RUN
     F************************************************** VJBR40 **
     FAB#PP66 UP  E                    DISK
     FAB#PP66BO   E                    DISK
     F            AB#PP661                          KRENAMEAB#PP66X
      *
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PYMD    8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   9        BEFORE
     C                     PARM           PKENS   9        AFTER
     C                     MOVE PYMD      WYMD    80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   90
     C           A6NYMD    IFLE WYMD
     C                     WRITEAB#PP66X
     C                     DELETAB#PP661
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   90
     C                     END
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
